[[html]]
<style type="text/css" id="internal-style">
                    @import url(http://d3g0gp89917ko0.cloudfront.net/v--3e7a7facf318/common--theme/base/css/style.css);
                    @import url(http://d3g0gp89917ko0.cloudfront.net/v--3e7a7facf318/common--theme/shiny/css/style.css);
                    @import url(http://scpsandbox-jp.wdfiles.com/local--theme/shiny/style.css);
</style>

<style type="text/css">
.vertical{
  -moz-transform: matrix(-1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0);
  -webkit-transform: matrix(-1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0);
  -ms-transform:matrix(-1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0);
  -o-transform:matrix(-1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0);
  transform:matrix(-1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0);
  text-align:right;
}
.horizon{
  -moz-transform: matrix(1, 0, 0, -1, 0, 0);
  -webkit-transform: matrix(1, 0, 0, -1, 0, 0);
  -ms-transform:matrix(1, 0, 0, -1, 0, 0);
  -o-transform:matrix(1, 0, 0, -1, 0, 0);
  transform:matrix(1, 0, 0, -1, 0, 0);
}
</style>

<SCRIPT language="javascript">
function random_display(){
  var i = 0;
  var n = 0;
  while(i < 13){
 //   document.write(n);
    n +=1;
    var elem = document.getElementById("block"+n);
    var rr = Math.round(Math.random()*10)+1;
    if(rr % 2 == 0){
      elem.className = "horizon";
    }else{
      elem.className = "vertical";
    }
  i++;
  }
}

</SCRIPT>

<div id ="block1" class="normal"><b>20██/██/██，回收于██小学小学图书室的文件</b></div>
<blockquote>
<div id ="block2" class="normal">钟声在不知不觉间不断响彻。睿智的代价是永不停息的历史。充斥着逃亡和生存的历史不知不觉变成了由掠夺和杀戮组成的连锁。我们有罪过。我们有过错。我们有憎恶。</div>
<div id ="block3" class="normal">进化是噩梦。文化是噩梦。历史是噩梦。胎儿的梦境，也是噩梦。</div>
<div id ="block4" class="normal">钟声不断响彻。镌刻在螺旋上的记忆、进化、文化、历史是无始无终的噩梦。</div>
<div id ="block5" class="normal">遮住眼睛塞住耳朵伫立着憎恶变得巨大，成为下一个胎儿的梦境。</div>
<div id ="block6" class="normal">没有结束。不会断绝。不会被宽恕。</div>
<br>
<div id ="block7" class="normal">钟声不会停止。进化的尽头没有结束。</div>
<div id ="block8" class="normal">人世会毁灭。在进化的尽头人世的毁灭终将造访。</div>
<div id ="block9" class="normal">下一个胎儿会继承睿智的代价。鸟的、花的、兽的胎儿也会做梦吧。</div>
<br>
<div id ="block10" class="normal">我只是，想忘记而已。</div>
</blockquote>

<SCRIPT language="javascript">
window.onload = function(){
setInterval('random_display()',50000);
}
</SCRIPT>

[[/html]]
